WEBVTT

00:00:00.560 --> 00:00:02.710
Well, good evening, family. Thank you

00:00:02.720 --> 00:00:04.950
for joining me again today. We really

00:00:04.960 --> 00:00:06.710
appreciate y'all always showing up and

00:00:06.720 --> 00:00:09.509
praying with us. It's such a

00:00:09.519 --> 00:00:12.230
blessing. We really prayed hard last

00:00:12.240 --> 00:00:14.390
night and I believe we've seen a

00:00:14.400 --> 00:00:16.790
lot of results, all to the glory of God.

00:00:16.800 --> 00:00:19.109
Isn't that amazing? It's

00:00:19.119 --> 00:00:23.029
kind of like putting a fire out.

00:00:23.039 --> 00:00:24.150
It's like you have a fire

00:00:24.160 --> 00:00:25.830
extinguisher and you can see it kind of

00:00:25.840 --> 00:00:28.950
going across the world—a defusing of

00:00:28.960 --> 00:00:31.029
things right now. You can see all the

00:00:31.039 --> 00:00:33.110
things that are happening in the world

00:00:33.120 --> 00:00:35.110
right now with all the major articles

00:00:35.120 --> 00:00:37.350
that Braden found today, with even

00:00:37.360 --> 00:00:40.150
President Trump and Israel saying don't

00:00:40.160 --> 00:00:42.790
strike Iran right now and the other

00:00:42.800 --> 00:00:44.709
Arab nations. And I thought, well, isn't

00:00:44.719 --> 00:00:47.670
that interesting? It felt like

00:00:47.680 --> 00:00:50.950
it was a volcano that

00:00:50.960 --> 00:00:53.590
was getting ready to explode yesterday

00:00:53.600 --> 00:00:55.910
as I was interceding all day long.

00:00:55.920 --> 00:00:57.750
We could feel the pressure of this thing

00:00:57.760 --> 00:00:59.430
mounting and mounting.

00:01:01.359 --> 00:01:03.430
It was to the point where I told

00:01:03.440 --> 00:01:06.070
Diana, 'This thing is about to

00:01:06.080 --> 00:01:09.510
go off right now.'It felt so

00:01:09.520 --> 00:01:11.429
imminent, but the Lord

00:01:14.479 --> 00:01:16.390
said, 'This can't be done by

00:01:16.400 --> 00:01:17.670
yourself. You're going to have to have

00:01:17.680 --> 00:01:20.230
corporate

00:01:20.230 --> 00:01:20.240
intercession.'So

00:01:20.240 --> 00:01:22.950
He said, 'Bring it to the people and

00:01:22.960 --> 00:01:26.310
pray last night over

00:01:26.320 --> 00:01:28.789
what we were seeing.'And so that's what

00:01:28.799 --> 00:01:31.830
we did. I want to show you some

00:01:31.840 --> 00:01:33.910
of the articles that came in the news

00:01:33.920 --> 00:01:37.910
today that Braden found that I

00:01:37.920 --> 00:01:40.310
believe are a result of all of us

00:01:40.320 --> 00:01:43.190
praying. You had the WWPs praying

00:01:43.200 --> 00:01:46.230
with Sister Billy and her group,

00:01:46.240 --> 00:01:49.190
and there's a lot of

00:01:49.200 --> 00:01:50.870
you that come from over there to

00:01:50.880 --> 00:01:53.030
our

00:01:53.040 --> 00:01:54.469
broadcast, and we're so grateful for

00:01:54.479 --> 00:01:57.910
every single one of you. I want to

00:01:57.910 --> 00:01:57.920
show...

00:01:57.920 --> 00:01:59.670
do you have any of those

00:01:59.680 --> 00:02:00.789
articles?

00:02:00.799 --> 00:02:01.350
Yes.

00:02:01.360 --> 00:02:03.510
Germany. This is what I thought

00:02:03.520 --> 00:02:05.510
was kind of interesting. Remember I told

00:02:05.520 --> 00:02:07.030
you when I was looking in the spirit, I

00:02:07.040 --> 00:02:09.910
felt, 'Don't—you're going to escalate this

00:02:09.920 --> 00:02:13.110
if he goes after NATO... if he goes after

00:02:13.110 --> 00:02:13.120
Greenland.'I

00:02:13.120 --> 00:02:15.910
felt

00:02:15.920 --> 00:02:18.229
such a

00:02:18.239 --> 00:02:20.150
red light, green

00:02:20.160 --> 00:02:22.229
light, and the Lord was showing us this

00:02:22.239 --> 00:02:25.270
is going to burn bridges so greatly

00:02:25.280 --> 00:02:29.190
with Europe if he does this. Now, a lot of

00:02:29.200 --> 00:02:30.869
people say, 'I don't care

00:02:30.879 --> 00:02:32.869
if he burns bridges or not.'Go back

00:02:32.879 --> 00:02:36.070
to that article. 'Germany and other

00:02:36.080 --> 00:02:39.509
NATO allies sending troops to Greenland

00:02:39.509 --> 00:02:39.519
amid

00:02:39.519 --> 00:02:42.150
Trump

00:02:42.150 --> 00:02:42.160
threats.'So

00:02:42.160 --> 00:02:45.030
they're sending troops to defend

00:02:45.040 --> 00:02:46.550
Greenland

00:02:46.560 --> 00:02:50.710
against the United States of America.

00:02:50.720 --> 00:02:53.190
And I thought, that says

00:02:53.190 --> 00:02:53.200
something—that

00:02:53.200 --> 00:02:57.430
our allies are sending

00:02:57.440 --> 00:03:01.589
their troops to defend a nation against

00:03:01.599 --> 00:03:03.670
us because I said it will come across as

00:03:03.680 --> 00:03:07.750
a bully. I said this will affect

00:03:07.760 --> 00:03:10.149
the

00:03:10.159 --> 00:03:12.550
midterms;

00:03:12.560 --> 00:03:15.830
I saw this affecting midterms and it was

00:03:15.840 --> 00:03:17.990
very negative. There's a lot of

00:03:18.000 --> 00:03:19.190
people who said, 'Brandon, I just don't

00:03:19.200 --> 00:03:20.630
believe that we'll lose any kind of

00:03:20.640 --> 00:03:22.550
seats in the House or the Senate. We're

00:03:22.560 --> 00:03:25.110
going to do a landslide home run again

00:03:25.120 --> 00:03:27.750
just like we did in 2024. We're going to

00:03:27.760 --> 00:03:29.830
do it in 2026 and we're

00:03:29.840 --> 00:03:31.910
just going to do all

00:03:31.910 --> 00:03:31.920
this.'I

00:03:31.920 --> 00:03:34.309
said this is

00:03:34.319 --> 00:03:36.070
where the Lord said, 'Don't underestimate

00:03:36.080 --> 00:03:38.789
your enemy.

00:03:38.799 --> 00:03:40.789
Don't underestimate

00:03:40.799 --> 00:03:43.830
the darkness on both

00:03:43.830 --> 00:03:43.840
sides.'I'm

00:03:43.840 --> 00:03:44.710
not going to sit here and say everything

00:03:44.710 --> 00:03:44.720
is

00:03:44.720 --> 00:03:46.390
always bright and sunny on

00:03:46.400 --> 00:03:48.710
the Republican side, but

00:03:48.720 --> 00:03:51.509
I'm going to tell you, for the most part,

00:03:51.519 --> 00:03:53.509
a lot of the way that the Republicans

00:03:53.519 --> 00:03:57.750
vote is biblical Christian values,

00:03:57.760 --> 00:04:00.149
and so that's why we always sway that

00:04:00.159 --> 00:04:02.869
way. But

00:04:02.879 --> 00:04:04.149
the Lord said, 'Don't

00:04:04.159 --> 00:04:08.869
underestimate your enemy. You must pray

00:04:08.879 --> 00:04:12.149
for President Trump to finish his term.

00:04:12.159 --> 00:04:15.190
You must pray for him to finish, live

00:04:15.200 --> 00:04:17.509
long, finish strong, and not just

00:04:17.519 --> 00:04:19.430
barely getting by, but

00:04:19.430 --> 00:04:19.440
flourish.'There

00:04:19.440 --> 00:04:22.469
was a major door last

00:04:22.479 --> 00:04:24.710
night that we were seeing when we got

00:04:24.720 --> 00:04:29.189
up to it. I saw this major door

00:04:29.199 --> 00:04:31.189
that was a beautiful door. It was

00:04:31.199 --> 00:04:33.510
glowing with all this beautiful light,

00:04:33.520 --> 00:04:35.749
but it was a door for only Trump to go

00:04:35.759 --> 00:04:37.350
through. It

00:04:37.350 --> 00:04:37.360
involved

00:04:37.360 --> 00:04:39.590
major decisions that he was

00:04:39.600 --> 00:04:42.310
going to make to get through this door.

00:04:42.320 --> 00:04:45.670
But in front of this door was

00:04:45.680 --> 00:04:50.310
a black fence that had briars and

00:04:50.320 --> 00:04:54.710
rose bush thorns wrapped into it,

00:04:54.720 --> 00:04:57.030
and we had to

00:04:57.040 --> 00:04:59.670
cut it back. I know it's symbolic,

00:04:59.680 --> 00:05:01.670
okay? It's not a real door.

00:05:01.680 --> 00:05:03.270
For all you baby

00:05:03.280 --> 00:05:05.030
Christians that are just coming on here,

00:05:05.040 --> 00:05:06.469
this is not a real door; this is a

00:05:06.479 --> 00:05:07.990
spiritual door. There's something in the

00:05:08.000 --> 00:05:09.430
spirit realm the Lord's trying to show

00:05:09.440 --> 00:05:12.070
us. So we are

00:05:12.080 --> 00:05:14.710
opening that door

00:05:14.720 --> 00:05:17.510
by faith, praying over whatever this

00:05:17.520 --> 00:05:19.830
door is that the Father has for

00:05:19.840 --> 00:05:22.070
President Trump. As

00:05:22.070 --> 00:05:22.080
for

00:05:22.080 --> 00:05:24.550
the briars, we prune

00:05:24.560 --> 00:05:26.310
them back. We're taking everything off,

00:05:26.320 --> 00:05:27.990
opening and making the gate

00:05:28.000 --> 00:05:29.670
possible to get through in the spirit

00:05:29.680 --> 00:05:31.430
realm.

00:05:31.440 --> 00:05:33.990
All this is bathed in prayer; this is

00:05:34.000 --> 00:05:37.189
symbolic.

00:05:37.199 --> 00:05:40.710
So the Lord showed us that door and we

00:05:40.720 --> 00:05:43.350
were to undergird him in prayer by

00:05:43.360 --> 00:05:46.550
lifting his hands and praying over these

00:05:46.560 --> 00:05:48.390
doors that the Lord has for him. For He

00:05:48.400 --> 00:05:50.629
said, 'This is a door that I have

00:05:50.639 --> 00:05:52.070
presented for him, but you've got to obey

00:05:52.080 --> 00:05:53.990
this in prayer

00:05:54.000 --> 00:05:56.150
for a major

00:05:56.160 --> 00:05:58.629
assignment.'So

00:05:58.639 --> 00:06:00.150
we saw that door and we saw that

00:06:00.160 --> 00:06:01.350
assignment last night.

00:06:01.360 --> 00:06:03.430
I could see us hacking away

00:06:03.440 --> 00:06:05.430
with a machete in the spirit realm or

00:06:05.430 --> 00:06:05.440
a

00:06:05.440 --> 00:06:08.309
sword, cutting back those thorns and

00:06:08.319 --> 00:06:10.870
those briars so that he could walk

00:06:10.880 --> 00:06:12.629
through and do what he's supposed to do.

00:06:12.639 --> 00:06:14.950
That's what the body of Christ is

00:06:14.960 --> 00:06:16.710
called to do—to pray for our

00:06:16.720 --> 00:06:19.909
leadership. Pray for

00:06:19.919 --> 00:06:21.990
our governors, our mayors,

00:06:22.000 --> 00:06:24.870
our police department, whoever

00:06:24.870 --> 00:06:24.880
is

00:06:24.880 --> 00:06:26.629
protecting this. We pray for our

00:06:26.639 --> 00:06:29.029
leadership. And so that's what we did

00:06:29.039 --> 00:06:31.749
last night. We saw that, and then I

00:06:31.759 --> 00:06:33.749
saw again

00:06:33.759 --> 00:06:36.629
the red light, green light. The

00:06:36.639 --> 00:06:40.070
Lord was showing me about the troops,

00:06:40.080 --> 00:06:42.950
praying for the troops, praying for the

00:06:42.960 --> 00:06:45.990
secret intel—our friends.

00:06:46.000 --> 00:06:48.550
The Lord will not allow me

00:06:48.560 --> 00:06:51.029
to say a lot of what I saw last night

00:06:51.039 --> 00:06:54.230
for the safety of our people who are

00:06:54.240 --> 00:06:57.590
trying to protect our nation.

00:06:57.600 --> 00:06:59.350
I'm

00:06:59.360 --> 00:07:01.029
just going to bypass it

00:07:01.039 --> 00:07:03.110
and move on because I don't

00:07:03.120 --> 00:07:05.510
want to get a spanking, and for

00:07:05.510 --> 00:07:05.520
their

00:07:05.520 --> 00:07:07.510
safety, it's just

00:07:07.510 --> 00:07:07.520
better.

00:07:07.520 --> 00:07:10.790
But okay, this is what we're

00:07:10.800 --> 00:07:12.150
going to do. We're going to go over some

00:07:12.160 --> 00:07:14.150
of these other articles. Do you have any

00:07:14.160 --> 00:07:17.510
more articles?

00:07:17.520 --> 00:07:21.350
'Israel and Arab nations

00:07:21.350 --> 00:07:21.360
ask

00:07:21.360 --> 00:07:23.990
Trump to refrain from attacking Iran for

00:07:24.000 --> 00:07:27.189
right

00:07:27.189 --> 00:07:27.199
now.'I

00:07:27.199 --> 00:07:29.189
thought that was interesting. That's

00:07:29.199 --> 00:07:31.749
what I'm saying. That's a—I believe that

00:07:31.759 --> 00:07:35.670
is a defusing and trying to, because

00:07:35.680 --> 00:07:37.589
of what they're getting on the ground, us

00:07:37.599 --> 00:07:40.230
praying for the people that are in

00:07:40.240 --> 00:07:43.749
harm's way. And this

00:07:43.759 --> 00:07:46.309
article could be old news right

00:07:46.309 --> 00:07:46.319
now—I

00:07:46.319 --> 00:07:48.070
don't know when he got

00:07:48.550 --> 00:07:48.560
this—but

00:07:49.520 --> 00:07:51.110
it just came out

00:07:51.120 --> 00:07:54.150
today. So,

00:07:54.160 --> 00:07:56.070
very interesting. Any other news?

00:07:56.080 --> 00:07:59.990
Then you had Russia.

00:08:26.479 --> 00:08:29.029
Russia says blackmail and threats

00:08:29.039 --> 00:08:32.630
against Cuba are unacceptable.

00:08:32.640 --> 00:08:36.630
We already know that I saw

00:08:36.640 --> 00:08:40.550
Russia reaching out to Cuba, trying to

00:08:40.560 --> 00:08:43.509
have an underground alliance like the

00:08:43.519 --> 00:08:45.829
1960s

00:08:45.839 --> 00:08:47.990
Cuban missile

00:08:48.000 --> 00:08:50.630
crisis. The Lord said, 'Watch old

00:08:50.640 --> 00:08:52.550
alliances,

00:08:52.560 --> 00:08:55.350
for they'll try to be

00:08:55.350 --> 00:08:55.360
rebirthed.'And

00:08:55.360 --> 00:08:58.389
I saw Russia giving biological

00:08:58.399 --> 00:09:02.630
weapons to Cuba and they put them

00:09:02.640 --> 00:09:06.070
underneath the ground in Cuba.

00:09:11.360 --> 00:09:14.710
I saw 50-gallon drums. I saw a

00:09:14.710 --> 00:09:14.720
vial—it

00:09:14.720 --> 00:09:17.590
looked like a cylinder

00:09:17.600 --> 00:09:20.310
sphere thing with a biohazard on it. And

00:09:20.320 --> 00:09:24.470
the Lord showed me this was a

00:09:24.480 --> 00:09:27.670
planned future attack through

00:09:27.680 --> 00:09:29.269
mules

00:09:29.279 --> 00:09:33.110
against America through Florida—down in

00:09:33.120 --> 00:09:36.470
Florida, Miami in particular. And so the

00:09:36.480 --> 00:09:38.630
Lord showed us all that. Well, we see

00:09:38.640 --> 00:09:41.030
Russia coming to bat for Cuba because

00:09:41.040 --> 00:09:43.190
they needed Cuba, but they wanted

00:09:43.200 --> 00:09:46.630
Venezuela. They wanted Colombia.

00:09:46.640 --> 00:09:48.870
They want all the alliance for the

00:09:48.870 --> 00:09:48.880
BRICS.

00:09:48.880 --> 00:09:51.190
But this is what I was seeing

00:09:51.200 --> 00:09:53.350
when we were diffusing and taking

00:09:53.360 --> 00:09:57.269
apart their

00:09:57.279 --> 00:10:00.389
foundation of what they wanted.

00:10:00.399 --> 00:10:02.870
Little by little,

00:10:02.880 --> 00:10:05.190
they get in a panic. It's putting the

00:10:05.200 --> 00:10:08.230
bear in a corner. And I saw us poking

00:10:08.240 --> 00:10:10.070
the bear. Remember how many times I said,

00:10:10.080 --> 00:10:12.710
'Be careful poking the

00:10:12.710 --> 00:10:12.720
bear.'As

00:10:12.720 --> 00:10:15.350
I saw President Trump cracking his

00:10:15.360 --> 00:10:17.590
whip, and in the visions in the past,

00:10:17.600 --> 00:10:20.069
he was standing on that stand and he was

00:10:20.079 --> 00:10:23.350
cracking his whip

00:10:23.360 --> 00:10:25.509
and he was making the bear pause and the

00:10:25.519 --> 00:10:28.550
dragon pause, and

00:10:28.560 --> 00:10:32.069
for this season, they

00:10:32.079 --> 00:10:33.910
were pausing. But the Lord said, 'Watch

00:10:33.920 --> 00:10:36.389
how they pause just for a

00:10:36.389 --> 00:10:36.399
season.'It

00:10:36.399 --> 00:10:38.949
doesn't mean that they stop forever.

00:10:38.959 --> 00:10:41.829
They just pause. A lion tamer can only

00:10:41.839 --> 00:10:45.509
get the lion to pause.

00:10:45.519 --> 00:10:47.910
And He said, 'I will use him right now

00:10:47.920 --> 00:10:50.550
to get some stuff done so that the body

00:10:50.560 --> 00:10:53.350
of Christ can move around and get things

00:10:53.360 --> 00:10:55.350
done more freely than what they could

00:10:55.360 --> 00:10:57.269
have if Kamala Harris would have been on

00:10:57.279 --> 00:10:59.110
the scene.

00:10:59.120 --> 00:11:02.949
I will use him to get the church ready

00:11:02.959 --> 00:11:05.750
for a major outpouring of My spirit for

00:11:05.760 --> 00:11:07.190
what you're about to see, for the

00:11:07.200 --> 00:11:08.949
greatest move of God we've ever seen

00:11:08.959 --> 00:11:10.069
before.'And

00:11:10.079 --> 00:11:13.190
I saw the Lord using him again for

00:11:13.200 --> 00:11:15.030
finances as he was pedaling at the

00:11:15.040 --> 00:11:16.710
canoe trying to keep the economy from

00:11:16.720 --> 00:11:19.030
going over the side.

00:11:19.040 --> 00:11:22.630
They said, 'Brandon, you say a

00:11:22.640 --> 00:11:24.470
lot of stuff about the economy. You say,

00:11:24.480 --> 00:11:25.829
"How come we haven't seen

00:11:25.829 --> 00:11:25.839
anything?"'Then

00:11:25.839 --> 00:11:28.069
this is Satan's wheelhouse.

00:11:28.079 --> 00:11:31.430
This is what he's best at is finances.

00:11:31.440 --> 00:11:33.430
And this is not going to take somebody

00:11:33.440 --> 00:11:36.470
being limp-wristed, sitting there being

00:11:36.480 --> 00:11:38.069
idly getting by going, 'Well, God,

00:11:38.079 --> 00:11:39.350
you're just going to rain it down on

00:11:39.350 --> 00:11:39.360
me.'You

00:11:39.360 --> 00:11:42.389
have to... The Lord said, 'If you

00:11:42.399 --> 00:11:44.069
want

00:11:44.079 --> 00:11:45.910
this next wealth transfer, you're going

00:11:45.920 --> 00:11:49.110
to have to contend for

00:11:49.110 --> 00:11:49.120
it.'Be

00:11:49.120 --> 00:11:51.670
a contender.

00:11:51.680 --> 00:11:54.310
How bad do you want it? How bad are you

00:11:54.320 --> 00:11:57.030
willing to pray and come against because

00:11:57.040 --> 00:11:59.670
we are in the end of the end?

00:11:59.680 --> 00:12:01.829
How bad do you want the wealth transfer?

00:12:01.839 --> 00:12:03.590
How bad do you want it, church? You're

00:12:03.600 --> 00:12:05.829
not just going to sit idly by and pluck

00:12:05.839 --> 00:12:07.590
it like ripe cherries off a

00:12:07.600 --> 00:12:10.069
tree. The Lord showed me that you're

00:12:10.079 --> 00:12:13.269
going to have to be listening to Him

00:12:13.279 --> 00:12:15.350
every single step of the way. Listening

00:12:15.360 --> 00:12:17.269
to the Father's voice so that you don't

00:12:17.279 --> 00:12:19.190
hear the stranger's voice on when to

00:12:19.200 --> 00:12:21.269
invest, what to invest in, and when to

00:12:21.279 --> 00:12:23.350
get out. Know when to hold them, know

00:12:23.360 --> 00:12:24.710
when to fold them, know when to walk

00:12:24.720 --> 00:12:26.069
away, know when to run. Like Kenny

00:12:26.079 --> 00:12:28.710
Rogers, you've got to count your

00:12:28.720 --> 00:12:30.628
money when you're sitting at the table.

