try to be or whatever you think you're

01:08:28.000 --> 01:08:29.990
dealing with—you have a bad marriage, a

01:08:30.000 --> 01:08:32.229
bad boss, a bad workplace, a bad

01:08:32.239 --> 01:08:34.630
environment, whatever—Father, I thank

01:08:34.640 --> 01:08:36.870
you, Lord, that if you can use me, use

01:08:36.880 --> 01:08:39.189
me.

01:08:39.199 --> 01:08:42.630
Whatever you can use, Father, if you can

01:08:42.640 --> 01:08:46.229
use me, use me.

01:08:46.239 --> 01:08:49.269
Here am I, Lord, send me. Here am I,

01:08:49.279 --> 01:08:52.070
Lord. Use me.

01:08:52.080 --> 01:08:55.349
If you can use this old flesh,

01:08:55.359 --> 01:08:57.430
if you can use Brandon, if you can use

01:08:57.440 --> 01:09:00.149
Braden and Diana and my daughters,

01:09:00.159 --> 01:09:03.749
Father, I thank you. If you can use me,

01:09:03.759 --> 01:09:08.470
if you can use anyone, Lord, use me.

01:09:08.480 --> 01:09:12.070
Help me, Father.

01:09:12.080 --> 01:09:13.590
But there are so many of you that

01:09:13.590 --> 01:09:13.600
I've

01:09:13.600 --> 01:09:17.110
seen tonight who are not

01:09:17.120 --> 01:09:19.590
baptized in the Holy Ghost, who don't

01:09:19.600 --> 01:09:21.189
understand it

01:09:21.189 --> 01:09:21.199
and

01:09:21.199 --> 01:09:23.910
don't have any clue. That's why I

01:09:23.920 --> 01:09:25.189
always tell you to get the book Why

01:09:25.199 --> 01:09:27.829
Tongues by Kenneth

01:09:27.829 --> 01:09:27.839
E. Hagin

01:09:27.839 --> 01:09:29.430
and read that book over and over and

01:09:29.440 --> 01:09:31.510
over again. It's a little bitty book;

01:09:31.520 --> 01:09:33.189
read it over and over again. I have

01:09:33.199 --> 01:09:36.070
some of them lying around here, and

01:09:36.080 --> 01:09:39.510
just read it and meditate on that word.

01:09:39.520 --> 01:09:41.189
It will change you from the inside out.

01:09:41.199 --> 01:09:43.590
It's out in the garage, son. I'm sure

01:09:43.590 --> 01:09:43.600
I've

01:09:43.600 --> 01:09:45.430
got it; it's on my bookshelf.

01:09:45.440 --> 01:09:47.030
"What is it?""The

01:09:47.030 --> 01:09:47.040
guy."No,

01:09:47.040 --> 01:09:50.070
I was talking about Why Tongues by

01:09:50.070 --> 01:09:50.080
Kenneth

01:09:50.080 --> 01:09:51.749
E.

01:09:51.749 --> 01:09:51.759
Hagin.

01:09:51.759 --> 01:09:55.030
"Oh, I can find

01:09:55.030 --> 01:09:55.040
it."If

01:09:55.040 --> 01:09:56.550
you... I was going to show them what it

01:09:56.560 --> 01:10:00.870
looked like, but it doesn't matter.

01:10:00.880 --> 01:10:03.189
So, I try to encourage you all

01:10:03.199 --> 01:10:04.709
because it's so important that

01:10:04.719 --> 01:10:07.430
you're able to shake it off.

01:10:07.440 --> 01:10:09.189
Don't allow the devil to just keep

01:10:09.199 --> 01:10:10.790
beating you down and making you feel

01:10:10.800 --> 01:10:13.910
like you can't do

01:10:13.910 --> 01:10:13.920
anything.

01:10:13.920 --> 01:10:17.590
He'll continually bring up your past and

01:10:17.600 --> 01:10:19.750
bring up your present—how you messed

01:10:19.760 --> 01:10:21.590
up just a couple minutes ago—and tell

01:10:21.600 --> 01:10:24.390
you there's nothing you can do. But as

01:10:24.400 --> 01:10:25.990
I'm praying, I've been seeing an

01:10:26.000 --> 01:10:27.669
earthquake.

01:10:27.679 --> 01:10:30.070
As I have been praying, I'm seeing a

01:10:30.080 --> 01:10:31.910
major earthquake coming out by the

01:10:31.920 --> 01:10:34.390
water. I'm seeing the earthquake and my

01:10:34.400 --> 01:10:38.630
son just put it up there; it's a 6.0

01:10:38.630 --> 01:10:38.640
that

01:10:38.640 --> 01:10:42.070
just happened.

01:10:42.640 --> 01:10:44.149
You all need to understand we're

01:10:44.159 --> 01:10:46.950
about to see something huge. As he put

01:10:46.960 --> 01:10:50.149
this up there, I was focused

01:10:50.159 --> 01:10:53.030
on it. It's amazing, son. This is the

01:10:53.040 --> 01:10:54.550
earthquake I've been seeing outside of

01:10:54.560 --> 01:10:56.790
Portland. This is 6.0 underneath that

01:10:56.800 --> 01:11:00.630
water.

01:11:00.640 --> 01:11:03.270
It's coming.

01:11:03.280 --> 01:11:06.229
I see major earthquakes coming. But the

01:11:06.239 --> 01:11:07.590
Lord said—because I was going to get

01:11:07.600 --> 01:11:09.430
off on the trail of that, but he

01:11:09.430 --> 01:11:09.440
said—I

01:11:09.440 --> 01:11:13.030
want you. There are so many of them that

01:11:13.040 --> 01:11:15.590
have so much potential to do much more

01:11:15.600 --> 01:11:18.390
for me than what they're doing,

01:11:18.400 --> 01:11:19.990
but they don't have anybody speaking

01:11:20.000 --> 01:11:22.550
life into them, son.

01:11:22.560 --> 01:11:24.310
And I was going to go on the road

01:11:24.320 --> 01:11:25.590
of telling you what I was seeing right

01:11:25.600 --> 01:11:28.390
then, but I was so focused. I want

01:11:28.400 --> 01:11:32.254
you to be prayers of precision

01:11:33.120 --> 01:11:35.270
so that when you come on this channel,

01:11:35.280 --> 01:11:37.590
we march to the beat of the same drum

01:11:37.600 --> 01:11:38.950
instead of sitting there going, "Man,

01:11:38.960 --> 01:11:40.630
I'm here. I want to add my supply, but I

01:11:40.640 --> 01:11:41.830
don't know what I'm going to do. I don't

01:11:41.840 --> 01:11:43.830
know how to help him."There

01:11:43.830 --> 01:11:43.840
are

01:11:43.840 --> 01:11:45.990
so many believers on here that

01:11:46.000 --> 01:11:48.390
are just so hungry and thirsty,

01:11:48.400 --> 01:11:50.149
and you want to come up higher in your

01:11:50.159 --> 01:11:52.149
prayer life and you want intimacy with

01:11:52.159 --> 01:11:53.270
the Father, and you're always telling me,

01:11:53.270 --> 01:11:53.280
"Brandon,

01:11:53.280 --> 01:11:55.590
I want to know Jesus so bad.

01:11:55.600 --> 01:11:57.350
Can I have a relationship with him like

01:11:57.360 --> 01:11:58.870
you?"This

01:11:58.880 --> 01:12:01.750
is how Brandon did it: I got a book

01:12:01.760 --> 01:12:04.630
like this, Why Tongues by Kenneth

01:12:04.630 --> 01:12:04.640
E. Hagin.

01:12:04.640 --> 01:12:07.110
And I read it and read it until

01:12:07.120 --> 01:12:10.310
it became real to me. There are only

01:12:10.320 --> 01:12:13.189
31 pages in this. And

01:12:13.199 --> 01:12:15.189
they're little bitty reads, but I read

01:12:15.199 --> 01:12:17.430
this over and over and over again. And

01:12:17.440 --> 01:12:20.149
you can find it for free online.

01:12:24.719 --> 01:12:28.229
How bad do you want change in your life?

01:12:28.239 --> 01:12:30.229
I said, "God, I want to be used."But it

01:12:30.239 --> 01:12:31.590
came out of the baptism of the Holy

01:12:31.600 --> 01:12:33.110
Ghost; I started praying in

01:12:33.110 --> 01:12:33.120
tongues.

01:12:33.120 --> 01:12:35.270
And the more I prayed in

01:12:35.270 --> 01:12:35.280
tongues,

01:12:35.280 --> 01:12:37.350
the more the Holy Ghost became real. The

01:12:37.360 --> 01:12:40.870
Holy Spirit became real to me. And I

01:12:40.880 --> 01:12:43.430
tell you, he is as real to me as my

01:12:43.440 --> 01:12:47.590
family is. He is barrel-chested. He is

01:12:47.600 --> 01:12:52.149
massive. He's green.

01:12:52.159 --> 01:12:55.910
He looks alive. There's life in him.

01:12:55.920 --> 01:12:57.910
I don't know how else to describe what I

01:12:57.920 --> 01:13:01.750
saw, but he is thick, barrel-chested,

01:13:01.750 --> 01:13:01.760
looked

01:13:01.760 --> 01:13:04.470
like a man. The silhouette of him

01:13:04.480 --> 01:13:06.870
appeared and I saw

01:13:06.880 --> 01:13:08.630
green.

01:13:08.640 --> 01:13:12.070
He looked like life.

01:13:12.080 --> 01:13:13.910
I know that sounds really crazy

01:13:13.920 --> 01:13:16.470
to the natural mind and you go, "Man,

01:13:16.480 --> 01:13:18.390
this guy's high on something."No, I'm

01:13:18.400 --> 01:13:22.550
telling you, God is alive.

01:13:22.560 --> 01:13:25.030
He's alive. The Holy Spirit's alive. But

01:13:25.040 --> 01:13:27.430
I want you to understand that you have

01:13:27.440 --> 01:13:29.270
the ability to pray in tongues and you

01:13:29.280 --> 01:13:30.870
can have a relationship with the Father,

01:13:30.880 --> 01:13:33.030
too. And I know that may sound really

01:13:33.040 --> 01:13:34.470
wild what I just said, and I'm not

01:13:34.480 --> 01:13:36.950
trying to weird you out. I'm just trying

01:13:36.960 --> 01:13:39.030
to tell you that there's more to

01:13:39.040 --> 01:13:41.750
a relationship with God than just

01:13:41.760 --> 01:13:43.350
feeling sorry for yourself. "God, help.

01:13:43.360 --> 01:13:45.669
Just use me, Lord. I'm just a worm.

01:13:45.679 --> 01:13:47.510
I'm just

01:13:47.510 --> 01:13:47.520
dust."Oh,

01:13:47.520 --> 01:13:49.750
you're created in his

01:13:49.760 --> 01:13:51.830
image.

01:13:51.840 --> 01:13:54.149
And he wants a relationship with you more

01:13:54.159 --> 01:13:58.149
than you want a relationship with him.

01:13:58.159 --> 01:14:00.790
Do you understand?

01:14:00.800 --> 01:14:02.950
I try to bring God to make him real to

01:14:02.960 --> 01:14:05.189
you as he is real to

01:14:05.199 --> 01:14:07.990
me. I don't have fakeness.

01:14:08.000 --> 01:14:09.669
I tell him all the

01:14:09.669 --> 01:14:09.679
time—I

01:14:09.679 --> 01:14:11.110
was ticked off this morning about some

01:14:11.120 --> 01:14:13.430
things that were happening last night, and

01:14:13.440 --> 01:14:16.630
I get upset and I start going,

01:14:16.640 --> 01:14:19.189
"This is what I feel,"and I tell him and I

01:14:19.199 --> 01:14:20.310
communicate with him. I said, "So, what

01:14:20.320 --> 01:14:23.510
do you think?

01:14:23.520 --> 01:14:26.790
I'm irritated about this."And we talk

01:14:29.280 --> 01:14:31.910
like he's sitting right

01:14:31.920 --> 01:14:34.070
in the room with me. I'm not

01:14:34.080 --> 01:14:35.830
disrespectful, but I tell him, "This is

01:14:35.840 --> 01:14:37.189
what I'm ticked off about. This is what

01:14:37.199 --> 01:14:39.110
I'm dealing with. Help me."And every

01:14:39.120 --> 01:14:41.669
single time he brings peace, Brandon,

01:14:43.760 --> 01:14:46.310
because in his presence, there's peace.

01:14:46.320 --> 01:14:48.709
There's joy. There are all the things that

01:14:48.719 --> 01:14:50.709
I need for that day. And I sit there and

01:14:50.719 --> 01:14:53.750
he diffuses that irritation. He diffuses

01:14:53.760 --> 01:14:54.950
what I'm going through and says,

01:14:54.960 --> 01:14:56.550
"Brandon,

01:14:56.560 --> 01:14:59.510
I got the answer for you. I didn't tell

01:14:59.520 --> 01:15:02.149
you to do any of those things.

01:15:02.159 --> 01:15:04.870
That's your flesh. I told you to do

01:15:04.880 --> 01:15:07.189
this, this, and this, and you've

01:15:07.199 --> 01:15:08.870
deviated off course of what I've asked

01:15:08.880 --> 01:15:10.310
you to do."And the reason why is

01:15:10.320 --> 01:15:14.070
because of disobedience.

01:15:14.080 --> 01:15:16.070
Come back to what I've asked you to do.

01:15:16.080 --> 01:15:17.830
Come back to the things and stop

01:15:17.840 --> 01:15:19.430
deviating off of what I've told you to

01:15:19.440 --> 01:15:21.270
do on certain things in your life. And I

01:15:21.280 --> 01:15:25.350
say, "Okay, I got it."And that peace

01:15:25.360 --> 01:15:27.189
that passes all understanding will flood

01:15:27.199 --> 01:15:29.270
your heart. And you'll sit back and

01:15:29.280 --> 01:15:32.709
you'll go... I want

01:15:32.719 --> 01:15:34.790
to ask you: how do you live your life

01:15:34.800 --> 01:15:37.350
without him?

01:15:37.360 --> 01:15:39.430
Tell me, those of you that don't

01:15:39.440 --> 01:15:41.189
live with the Holy Spirit: how

01:15:41.199 --> 01:15:43.430
do you live your life without him? I

01:15:43.440 --> 01:15:45.189
can't picture my life without him. I

01:15:45.199 --> 01:15:48.870
need him every second of every day.

01:15:48.880 --> 01:15:51.110
I need him all the time. And what I'm

01:15:51.120 --> 01:15:52.470
trying to tell you is get books

01:15:52.480 --> 01:15:54.229
like this and read them

01:15:54.229 --> 01:15:54.239
and say,

01:15:54.239 --> 01:15:59.030
"Father, fill me with the Holy

01:15:59.030 --> 01:15:59.040
Ghost."That's

01:15:59.040 --> 01:16:02.149
the beginning stages of it. This

01:16:02.159 --> 01:16:03.910
is not the end of it; this is

01:16:03.920 --> 01:16:06.630
the beginning of it—being filled.

01:16:06.640 --> 01:16:09.990
Keep being filled. I want less of me and

01:16:10.000 --> 01:16:13.830
more of you. I decrease, you increase. To

01:16:13.840 --> 01:16:16.390
die to self. This is just entering the

01:16:16.400 --> 01:16:19.430
doorway.

01:16:19.440 --> 01:16:21.590
It's not the end. It's just the

01:16:21.600 --> 01:16:23.430
beginning. It's just starting the race.

01:16:23.440 --> 01:16:24.870
You're running the race...

01:16:26.400 --> 01:16:29.189
but I'm trying to help you.

01:16:29.199 --> 01:16:31.110
Christianity is more than just

01:16:31.120 --> 01:16:33.189
having salvation.

01:16:33.199 --> 01:16:37.110
There's intimacy with the salvation.

01:16:37.120 --> 01:16:39.350
You were once lost, but now you're found.

01:16:39.360 --> 01:16:41.110
But now that you're found, there's more

01:16:41.120 --> 01:16:43.750
in the doorway of it.

01:16:43.760 --> 01:16:45.990
I was once lost, but now I'm found. Was

01:16:46.000 --> 01:16:48.390
blind, but now I see. But what do I see?

01:16:48.400 --> 01:16:51.430
That there's more.

01:16:51.440 --> 01:16:55.110
He has more for me.

01:16:55.120 --> 01:16:57.189
Do you understand?

01:16:57.199 --> 01:16:59.270
People just find salvation and that's

01:16:59.280 --> 01:17:01.270
wonderful.

01:17:01.280 --> 01:17:06.070
But there's more than just salvation.

01:17:06.070 --> 01:17:06.080
It

01:17:06.080 --> 01:17:09.590
is "Amazing Grace"—how sweet

01:17:09.600 --> 01:17:14.310
the sound that saved a wretch like

01:17:14.320 --> 01:17:15.830
me.

01:17:15.840 --> 01:17:20.470
I once was lost, but now I'm found. Was

01:17:20.480 --> 01:17:26.470
blind, but now I see.

01:17:26.480 --> 01:17:28.630
But now what do I see? That there's more

01:17:28.640 --> 01:17:31.510
for me than just salvation. Salvation just

01:17:31.520 --> 01:17:34.229
got me to the

01:17:34.239 --> 01:17:36.790
door. He gave it all to me. Now what is

01:17:36.800 --> 01:17:40.630
in the side of that door?

01:17:40.630 --> 01:17:40.640
That

01:17:40.640 --> 01:17:42.550
is just getting into the

01:17:42.560 --> 01:17:44.470
door.

01:17:44.480 --> 01:17:46.070
Getting the baptism of the Holy Ghost is

01:17:46.080 --> 01:17:47.990
getting into the

01:17:48.000 --> 01:17:49.270
flow with the realm of the spirit and

01:17:49.280 --> 01:17:51.270
going to the rivers. There

01:17:51.270 --> 01:17:51.280
are

01:17:51.280 --> 01:17:53.189
rivers. There

01:17:53.189 --> 01:17:53.199
are

01:17:53.199 --> 01:17:56.070
rooms. There are places in the

01:17:56.080 --> 01:17:58.310
spirit that I am telling you that

01:17:58.320 --> 01:18:00.310
are over and above all that you dare ask

01:18:00.320 --> 01:18:02.550
when you tap over into them. But you get

01:18:02.560 --> 01:18:05.669
there by praying in the Holy Ghost.

01:18:05.679 --> 01:18:07.669
But a lot of people just camp

01:18:07.679 --> 01:18:09.510
around salvation

01:18:09.520 --> 01:18:11.430
and they build their tent around it

01:18:11.440 --> 01:18:13.510
and they got their Holy Ghost walls and

01:18:13.520 --> 01:18:15.430
you build your lumberjack

01:18:15.440 --> 01:18:17.590
walls of your Holy Ghost and you don't

01:18:17.600 --> 01:18:19.510
go anywhere bigger than just, I

01:18:19.520 --> 01:18:21.830
was once lost but now I'm found, and if you

01:18:21.830 --> 01:18:21.840
are

01:18:21.840 --> 01:18:25.110
doing that you are missing it.

01:18:25.120 --> 01:18:26.950
That was just the key to say I'm

01:18:26.950 --> 01:18:26.960
wall-to-wall

01:18:26.960 --> 01:18:29.590
Holy Ghost. Now take me and do

01:18:29.600 --> 01:18:34.229
something with this flesh.

01:18:34.239 --> 01:18:36.790
Create in me a clean heart. Make me

01:18:36.800 --> 01:18:40.709
more like you.

01:18:40.719 --> 01:18:42.950
We have this treasure. I keep saying it,

01:18:42.960 --> 01:18:45.669
but it is the refining

01:18:45.679 --> 01:18:49.030
fire that purifies us to make us the

01:18:49.040 --> 01:18:50.950
vessel that God wants to do something

01:18:50.960 --> 01:18:53.270
bigger with us.

01:18:53.280 --> 01:18:55.430
Does that make sense?

01:18:55.440 --> 01:18:57.590
But most people, like I said, the

01:18:57.600 --> 01:18:59.910
Baptists, good old Baptists, the

01:18:59.920 --> 01:19:01.270
Southern Baptists, they will teach you how

01:19:01.280 --> 01:19:03.430
to get saved, but they got to teach you

01:19:03.440 --> 01:19:06.950
how to fight the devil, too.

01:19:06.960 --> 01:19:08.790
To say, "Listen,

01:19:08.800 --> 01:19:11.430
thus far and no further. You're not

01:19:11.440 --> 01:19:13.830
robbing me of my peace. You're

01:19:13.840 --> 01:19:16.070
not robbing me."Because that is when you

01:19:16.080 --> 01:19:18.470
learn about the blood.

01:19:18.480 --> 01:19:20.950
What does the blood do? The blood never

01:19:20.960 --> 01:19:23.350
loses its power.

01:19:23.360 --> 01:19:26.310
The blood drives out devils. The blood. That

01:19:26.310 --> 01:19:26.320
is

01:19:26.320 --> 01:19:28.149
why the anointing oil when you

01:19:28.159 --> 01:19:29.910
dump oil on somebody, this represents

01:19:29.920 --> 01:19:33.350
the blood of Jesus. The blood set me

01:19:33.360 --> 01:19:35.590
free.

01:19:35.600 --> 01:19:38.070
I put the blood and I apply the blood.

01:19:38.080 --> 01:19:40.709
This is representation. I apply the

01:19:40.719 --> 01:19:43.590
blood over my house. I apply the blood

01:19:43.600 --> 01:19:46.870
over my mind. I apply the blood over

01:19:46.880 --> 01:19:49.110
my bed and over my house. There is

01:19:49.120 --> 01:19:52.790
no devil in hell that can come nigh me. I

01:19:52.800 --> 01:19:55.189
march around my house and I put it on my

01:19:55.199 --> 01:19:57.350
shoes and I say the bloodline is around

01:19:57.360 --> 01:19:59.270
here. Satan, you can't cross the

01:19:59.280 --> 01:20:02.390
bloodline. You can't touch my wife. You

01:20:02.400 --> 01:20:04.870
